Package io.mats3.matssocket.impl

Class ClusterStoreAndForward_SQL_DbMigrations

java.lang.Object
io.mats3.matssocket.impl.ClusterStoreAndForward_SQL_DbMigrations
public class ClusterStoreAndForward_SQL_DbMigrations extends Object
Perform the DB-setup/migrations that ClusterStoreAndForward_SQL needs, using Flyway. These needs to be run before the CSAF_SQL is booted up.
